Putting this thing in its own room seems a bit excessive to me. You could very easily just vacuum seal it and store it in a safe somewhere and it would be just as effective. Seeing as how the testing site is in another location you would have to seal it to move it anyways. 5 meters square is an awfully large place to house something that is at most about 1.5 meters long but more likely about 0.6 meters long. I mean SCP-108 is a person and it only gets 3m.

